cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "jiphyeonjeon-agent: An agent-native research MCP server for deep paper review"
abstract: >-
  An MCP (Model Context Protocol) server that exposes 집현전 (PaperReviewAgent)
  as native tools for Claude and other AI agents — semantic paper search across
  six sources (arXiv, Google Scholar, OpenAlex, DBLP, Connected Papers, OpenAlex
  Korean), deep multi-agent paper review, citation-graph exploration,
  learning-curriculum generation, and methodology-to-figure generation.
